## 🤖 AI Framework

### AI-001: AI Framework Architecture
- **Status**: ✅ Completed
- **Priority**: 🔴 Critical
- **Files**: `src/services/ai/types.ts`, `src/services/ai/abilityRegistry.ts`, `src/services/ai/aiClient.ts`, `src/services/ai/aiAuditService.ts`, `src/services/ai/aiDigestService.ts`, `src/services/ai/index.ts`
- **Issue**: AI abilities (briefing, reflection) were monolithic, no audit trail, no cost tracking, no extensibility.
- **Solution**: Created modular AI framework with central client, ability registry, audit service, digest service, and shared types. Every AI call flows through aiClient → audit log. New abilities added in 3 steps.
- **Completed Date**: 2026-03-26
- **Notes**: Framework structure: types.ts (shared types), abilityRegistry.ts (ability catalog + pricing), aiClient.ts (central caller), aiAuditService.ts (read/write audit), aiDigestService.ts (content digest CRUD)

