- **Status**: ✅ Completed
- **Priority**: 🟡 Medium
- **Files**: `src/App.tsx`, `src/components/MobileBottomNav.tsx`, `src/components/MobileContextHeader.tsx`, `src/components/SafeLockScreen.tsx`, `src/SafeView.tsx`, `src/components/AboutModal.tsx`, `src/components/FeaturesPage.tsx`, `index.html`, `public/features.json`
- **Issue**: "Safe" naming was confusing — Bank Records nested inside "Safe" wasn't obvious.
- **Solution**: Renamed all user-facing labels from "Safe" to "Vault". Internal code identifiers (SafeView, SafeEntry, etc.) kept unchanged to avoid massive refactoring.
